[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    124[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Cost estimate appears reasonable. Unlike Recipe 2.4 which had a multi-criterion loop, this pipeline is mostly a one-shot generation. At Claude Sonnet 4 pricing (~$3/M in, $15/M out), a generation call with ~2.5K input tokens and up to 6K output tokens is roughly $0.10. Add Haiku extraction (~$0.005) and optional Comprehend Medical (~$0.01). End-to-end $0.03-0.10 is defensible.[K
